Creating < 3 Min Graded and Grade Versatility goal slicer 40

Step 1

-Choose slicer from visualizations pane.

- Select value from the Number Table

- Make these change on the Format; Slicer heading =off, Title = On, Title Text = < 3min Goal, Title Background = #9071ce, Font Family = Constantia

Step 2

-Choose slicer from visualizations pane.

- Select value from the Number2 Table

- Make these change on the Format; Slicer heading =off, Title = On, Title Text = < 3min Goal, Title Background = #9071ce, Font Family = Constantia
